>\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=d0cd1ee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗衡中國魔掌<br />\n組建香港既遊說團隊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=1f36aef7\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=8bde528f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"6d9b3f0866753fb6964847e20524c20049d89175","tid":1672864,"uid":133320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T21:42:36.000Z","msg":"Vienna同prague 差不多<br />\nSalzburg 更悶<br />\n德國 走都方便"},{"pid":"fa45681f549c99047cceffe6ec80129e1349bb4e","tid":1672864,"uid":138999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"瑞-&gt;奧-&gt;德<br />\n唔好去GVA, 好悶, 唔去BERN, 留多一日玩zermatt, 6月行山正呀<br />\n<br />\n奧地利去Hallstatt, 國王湖, <br />\nCK同Hallstatt兩個鎮有d似, 考慮剩係去一個<br />\nSALZBURG除左駁腳去國王湖/Hallstatt冇乜特別, 除非好鐘意Mozart<br />\n唔去VIENNA, 除非想睇opera/聖堂/博物館<br />\n<br />\n德國去MUC, 天鵝堡, 一路玩上去FRA<br />\n<br />\n瑞-&gt;奧-&gt;意<br />\n意大利去Venice再由Milan走"},{"pid":"3011b739ce51c8be7415f10e415c0ec35a82dea9","tid":1672864,"uid":36034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"少女峰三日只係岩岩好，四日好d，行山都好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruOtvjk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruOtvjk.jpg&h=4af3475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WFvJEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WFvJEF.png&h=62fca6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Auhh76x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src